        Simple Container Management Tool

Requirements:

- coreutils
- qemu-kvm
- iproute
- sudo
- curl
- sed
- uml-utilities (tunctl)
- bridge-utils (brctl)
- bsdmainutils (hexdump)
- socat
- flock

Installation

On Debian systems:

# addgroup --system scmt
# install -m440 sudoers /etc/sudoers.d/scmt
# install -m755 scmt.sh /usr/bin/scmt
# install -d -m2770 -g scmt /var/lib/scmt

